<P>Si&thorn;en oure Lord Iesu Crist&meper; seide to his apostlis/ &thorn;at oone of|hem was a deuel&meper; &amp; ment it bi Iudas/ Be not &thorn;ise apostataas&meper; &thorn;at|don als yuel as he/ wor&thorn;i to be clepid deuelis&meper; bi &thorn;e same resoun?|&THORN;ei ben greet questioners&meper; &amp; askars of &thorn;e lawe/ but &thorn;ei wole not|do so miche&meper; as putt &thorn;erto her fynger/ &amp; &thorn;ei heepen charge on|o&thorn;ir&meper; more &thorn;an &thorn;ei mai bere/ &THORN;ei ben preisars of seintis&meper; &amp; no|&thorn;ing her folowars/ &thorn;ei ben heerars | of &thorn;e lawe&meper; but no &thorn;ing &thorn;e <MILESTONE UNIT="folio" N="88a">|doars/ &thorn;ei ben alwey lernyng&meper; &amp; neuir &thorn;ei wole be perfite/ &thorn;us &thorn;ei|boosten in &thorn;e lawe&meper; wi&thorn; worschip &amp; wi&thorn; wynnyng/ but bi breking|of &thorn;e lawe&meper; &thorn;ei don dispise her God &Verbar;</P></DIV3>
